sub_title: Adv. LLM Candidate in Law and Digital Technologies at Leiden University
summary: I am an admitted lawyer with five years of demonstrated experience in multinational companies and Big 4 consultancy firms. Most of my professional experience is centered in data protection at a multinational level, compliance control and contractual legal advisory per operational requirements. I consider myself a resourceful person with leadership skills guided by an empathic approach. I can work under pressure while being organized and finding pride in doing my best work at every task. I find value in being able to learn from mistakes and working as part of a team. I am currently finishing an Advanced Masters in Law and Digital Technologies in Leiden University (Class of 2023).
